    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The action of saying or doing something over again which one has already said or done. The term may be used in the context of visual images, the spoken or written word, performances, music, and other contexts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
